      <title>伊斯兰圣战组织发布了两名以色列男性人质恳求释放的视频</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/islamic-jihad-releases-video-two-male-israeli-hostages-pleading-their-release-2023-12-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战运动的武装组织圣城旅周二在其 Telegram 账户上发布了一段视频，视频中两名以色列男性人质恳求释放。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/islamic-jihad-releases-video-two-male-israeli-hostages-pleading-their-release-2023-12-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 21:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
